race.comment: BENNY THE BULL (2) has been out of the placings last two but shapes well for this if he can recapture his fast win a few runs back, getting around this track over 300m in 17.17. Looks the one to beat on best figures. NED (4) was below best last time at Cannington (22.05) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a 4.5 lengths fourth. Has already won two times from this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. ITA KEEPING (1) goes very well this trip starting 21 times for seven wins and four minors. Was out of placings last time (18.60) at this track in a Grade 4, finishing eighth and beaten 21 lengths. Among the main chances. ZATARA'S IMAGE (5) must be included in calculations. Something for the Multiples: BIG GIRL KIKI (8)
